snippet: The police are looking for a drug-smuggling gang that abandoned a 1,800-pound stash of marijuana on a southern beach.
abstract: Fifty-six bundles of marijuana turn up unclaimed on a beach in Greece; police are unclear whether drugs were brought in by sea or picked up by boat to be shipped elsewhere.
lead_paragraph: The police are looking for a drug-smuggling gang that abandoned a 1,800-pound stash of marijuana on a southern beach.

headline.main: Greece: Bundles of Marijuana Turn Up Unclaimed on a Beach
